begin
reserve K for Field;
theorem
Th6: (for a being (Element of K) holds (for x being (FinSequence of K) holds (( - ( a * x ) ) = ( ( - a ) * x ) & ( - ( a * x ) ) = ( a * ( - x ) ))))
proof
let a being (Element of K);
let x being (FinSequence of K);
set n = ( len x );
reconsider x0 = x as (Element of ( n -tuples_on (the carrier of K) )) by CKB3:1;
reconsider y = ( a * x0 ) as (Element of ( n -tuples_on (the carrier of K) ));
thus ( - ( a * x ) ) = ( ( - ( 1_ K ) ) * y ) by FVSUM_1:59
.= ( ( ( - ( 1_ K ) ) * a ) * x0 ) by FVSUM_1:54
.= ( ( - ( ( 1_ K ) * a ) ) * x0 ) by VECTSP_1:8
.= ( ( - a ) * x ) by VECTSP_1:def 8;
thus ( - ( a * x ) ) = ( ( - ( 1_ K ) ) * y ) by FVSUM_1:59
.= ( ( ( - ( 1_ K ) ) * a ) * x0 ) by FVSUM_1:54
.= ( a * ( ( - ( 1_ K ) ) * x0 ) ) by FVSUM_1:54
.= ( a * ( - x ) ) by FVSUM_1:59;
end;
